  "Species Y has more growth because of the larger IQR": "",
  "The species are essentially the same": "",
  "Species X has a slightly higher center (4.2 vs 4.0) and much smaller IQR (1.5 vs 5.8), meaning its growth is more consistent while Species Y varies widely.": "",
